<p>Today&#8217;s Macs do a lot more than the original Mac ever did, and some of that stuff happens without you knowing it. John and Dave start this conversation with some of the things they watch on their Macs to make sure nothing is happening that shouldn&#8217;t be. Dave also found a semi-solution to his dream podcasting setup, and talks through the details of that, as well!</p>
